data.description: Beautiful well maintain 3 beds 2.5 bath plus loft with built in shelves. High vaulted ceiling OPEN FLOOR PLAN living room with share fireplace with family room. Corian counter top kitchen NEW Carpet, fresh paint, newer appliances. Large size master bed with walk in closet & 5 pieces master bath. Stucco front & Concrete Tile Roof, Central A/C. Walk to park, close to school, convenience store, hwy 76, E470, Brighton Mall & more! Great place to live or investment!
data.whatILove: This home is just absolutely so welcoming when you walk in the door, very well lit, tall ceilings, super clean and ready to move in to.
